{"type":"message","id":"ebb91649","parentId":"3e61c6ec","timestamp":"2026-03-27T12:48:34.945Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've successfully completed the autonomous learning task. Let me summarize what was done.","thinkingSignature":"36a24e27f7ee802021193c5ffff2df3a244e840d4e8579fe67ee289173d2f160"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n✅ 自主学习完成（无活跃对话，自动执行）\n\n**完成内容：**\n- 搜索了企业数字化转型、智能安防、IT运维服务三个领域的最新动态\n- 整理了 **11条关键信息**，涵盖：\n  - AI多智能体系统（MAS）崛起\n  - 智能安防从\"被动告警\"向\"主动预判\"升级\n  - ITSS新版标准（GB/T 28827.1-2022）2026年强制执行\n- 已保存至 `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md`\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5306,"output":147,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49434,"cost":{"input":0.0015918,"output":0.0001764,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00308763}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774615707340}}
